    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my car, and it's been such a reliable companion! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road for many more miles. It drives super smooth and is perfect for anyone looking for a dependable ride without the brand-new price tag. I've kept up with it nicely, and I think you're really going to love how it handles. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to take it for a spin or have any questions at all\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 32500.0,
