      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2014 Porsche Cayman is a masterclass in mid-engine equilibrium, featuring a 2.7L naturally aspirated flat-six engine that excels in linear power delivery. The powertrain is mated to a lightning-fast 7-speed PDK dual-clutch transmission, ensuring seamless torque transfer and precise gear selection. Mechanically, the vehicle benefits from a low center of gravity and a rigid chassis architecture that minimizes torsional flex during high-G cornering. The suspension geometry remains tight, providing communicative feedback through the steering rack. Recent preventative maintenance ensures the cooling system and drivetrain seals are in excellent operational order. A driver-focused machine that prioritizes mechanical transparency and throttle response.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Clean title. Regular maintenance performed. Mechanically sound. Minimal wear.",
