    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality. The exterior retains a deep shine, though you\u2019ll find the expected minor road chips and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and exceptionally clean; the leather seats show light bolstering wear but remain supportive and free of any tears. All electronics, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is solid\u2014I have kept a detailed log of consistent oil changes and a recent brake pad replacement. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a reliable, comfortable experience for its next owner. This is an honest, dependable car ready for the road.",
      "price": 32500.0,
