      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 power plant featuring individual throttle bodies and a recent VANOS system refresh. This example boasts a true 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a reinforced rear subframe, addressing the chassis' known load-path vulnerabilities. The suspension has been enhanced with Bilstein dampers to maintain optimal tire contact patches through high-lateral-G cornering. With a recent valve clearance adjustment and documented maintenance history, this M3 remains a formidable performance machine for the discerning driver who values mechanical integrity over a concours finish.",
